Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The distance to the horizon seen at eye level\Nis roughly four kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do people around here suddenly start talking\Nto people they've never met?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you think I'm strange, by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're just annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's taboo for a high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Annoying," "uncool" and "can't take hints"\Nare the three big taboos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be sulking quite a bit.\NDid something bad happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shoko Makinohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makinohara spelled like Makinohara Rest Area,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Shoko spelled as "child soaring the skies."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, I've told you countless times,\Nstop crawling into my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you'd become aware\Nof the urge for forbidden love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, you should stop\Nbecause it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl that appeared that day\Nwith the abandoned cat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...had the same name as my first crush,\Nthe high school girl I met two years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shoko Makinohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had the same name...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet she didn't know anything about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two more weeks of summer break\Npassed with nothing happening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.\NWere you a good cat, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, the cat's name is now Hayate.\NFrom the Tohoku trains, like Nasuno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Though I said I'd like to adopt him,\NI haven't gotten around to asking my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of him for a while,\Nso it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Nasuno likes to have him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn how to take care of cats\Nat our place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, do you prefer\Nyour little sisters to be young?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you prefer them to be tidy and proper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Kaede is in the biggest crisis\Nin the history of Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a need to master the ways\Nof little sisterhood as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine having Kaede\Nas my one little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is Shoko-san to you, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makinohara, you don't have a big sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'm an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any relatives that look like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll consult Futaba, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AZUSAGAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Azusagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot if I keep my hair down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wearing glasses\Nbecause I have contacts on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why the school uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to school after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi's at work, so he's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Science Club is just me, so they'll\Nshut it down if I don't document activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met Shoko Makinohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That first crush of yours?\NShe really does exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, surprisingly enough,\Nshe's now a seventh grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it simply someone else\Nwith the same name and similar looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's said there are three people\Nwith the same face in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a popular urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, a common urban legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, this isn't causing you\Nactual harm for now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's a fireworks festival\Nsomewhere today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's one in Chigasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think it, you, me and Kunimi\Nwent to a fireworks festival last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were in normal clothes back then.\NYou should have worn a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I do something\Nso cumbersome for your sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to show Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I don't look good in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do yukatas not look good\Nwhen you got big boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd look pretty good if you wore a yukata\Nand had your hair the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.\NYou have to go to work, right? See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten more tanned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because I went to the beach\Ntwo days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Kamisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, how annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Says the guy with\Nan incredibly beautiful girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Mai-san is incredibly busy,\Nand I haven't seen her face all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her on TV yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I've seen her every day\Nif it's on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to brag about\Nyour cute yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because I didn't fill out\Nmy shifts for next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said that while staring at my breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was said in consideration to\Nthe balance between your waist and hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So irritating! Yeah yeah, I don't have breasts\Nbig enough to rest on top of the obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally cylindrical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welco—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you coming back\Nfrom your film shoot tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the show had a lot of veteran actors,\Nand I don't have outtakes, we finished early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you came back because\Nyou couldn't wait another day to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ready, I'll take your order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I realize I'm a horrible girlfriend too engrossed\Nwith work that she's ignoring her new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to what you'll do in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll do things for you within reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even lewd things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you came back early!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silly, you should have said that to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What time are you off?\NI'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dropping by every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Shoko Makinohara\Nwho looks exactly like your first crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is. Does that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'd be jealous of a seventh-grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything strange happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Futaba about it, too.\NNothing, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of talking about this,\NI want to make out with you a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you for a while, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that as much as you want later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I prefer we do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been inside a net café before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tell where she is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, lend me your smartphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you calling from a mobile number?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed Mai-san's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take your romantic talk elsewhere.\NSo what, another troublesome affair?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm equivalent to\Ntroublesome affairs in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Azusagawa, what's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, looks like the battery's dying,\NI'll call again later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't dodge this bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's been two Rio Futabas in the world\Nsince three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Adolescence Syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have taken care of it already, if I had any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So was it the other one that I met\Nat the bookstore this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I haven't seen you,\Nthat would be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That fake is inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's actually living in my house,\NI couldn't go there even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're at a net café?\NYou should have contacted me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, is it okay if I have Futaba\Nstay over at my place from today on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But Futaba's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be okay if I had\Na guy friend stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll stay at your place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother has brought\Nyet another new woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're ruining my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Kaede is your little sister,\Nand thus prepared to accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend, Rio Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Kaede Azusagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nasuno, and this is Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll both be staying with us\Nfor a while, starting tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Mai-san and Futaba\Ncan sleep in my room, and I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's sleep together\Nin Kaede's room, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denied. I'll sleep in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head home to grab some clothes,\Nand take a bath while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Futaba can bathe before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be clear, I don't intend on doing anything\Nto the Futaba broth bathwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should die at saying "broth."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave a towel here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have clothes to change into, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I can lend you\Na bunny girl outfit or panda pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just said I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you would leave, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you relaxing right outside the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about Adolescence Syndrome\Nwhen I asked "are you okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.\NJust to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slightly scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only slightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared\Nwhen I was alone in the net café.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, is something like this even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to exist as two people, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a possibility if quantum teleportation\Nworks on a macroscopic scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation?\NThat's only in movies, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite.\NI'm talking about in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We previously talked about\Nquantum entanglement, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apply it to this case\Nfor a simple explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say there's a blueprint with information\Non how to construct me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let's say you use quantum entanglement\Nto move that information to a distant location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, if we take Futaba who's in the bath at my\Nhouse, and send that information to the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The information that constructs me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will be established by someone's perception\Nin the guise of Rio Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With that logic, isn't it impossible\Nfor both to exist simultaneously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. In fact, I haven't seen\Nmy other self yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if you ask me if we both exist\Nsimultaneously, I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I met you at the net café,\NI was talking to the other Futaba on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you really talking to me on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see her or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but this quantum teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the information that\Nconstructs you is the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't your consciousness and memories\Nbe shared regardless of which is seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say the one observing me,\NRio Futaba, was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If, for whatever reason, there are two copies\Nof my consciousness that observes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we could end up in a situation\Nlike the right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning there are two personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that's true.\NHow did it end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watching Sakuta's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know you are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watching my boyfriend's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did your heart skip a beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in high spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get to spend time since a while ago\Nand sleep over at my boyfriend's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she hasn't slept peacefully\Nfor the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right in front of you,\Nyou're more worried about Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had the whole day off tomorrow,\Nso I planned on letting you take me on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking like that idea is a bust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're going to investigate\Nabout Futaba, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The "fake" should be at school tomorrow,\Nworking on Science Club things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, I was thinking about\Nheading over to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just want me to watch over the real Futaba\Nwhile you're checking out the fake one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected, Mai-san.\NYou really know me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be elated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ouch, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like you to. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in return for leaving you alone\Ndue to being busy with work, we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I'd like something in return\Njust to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here lying next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something more like\Nwhat birds do with beaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You didn't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to use an apology\Nas a reason to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you choose the right time, place and mood,\Nyou can make your move on me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you got bashful\Nand looked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you got too greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you suck at it, Sakuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that really hurts my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might lose confidence\Nand become scared of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'd never end up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll let you practice as much\Nas you need to until you can do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 3rd
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, this is delicious!\NIt's so fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The eggs are tasty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're so creamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Mai-san cook every day\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use Kaede as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My love is being tested right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it, Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that this is my first breakfast\Nin a while eating with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sakuta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have some guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite a few\Nfemale acquaintances, Sakuta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't mean anything by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rio Futaba,\Na classmate at my high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shoko Makinohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She really does exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think, Kunimi mentioned\Nthat there was a practice game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that a third-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's kinda sexy. Smart-sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kunimi doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came for my club activities,\Nand this was on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not do the "kyaaa! Kunimi!" thing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am cheering for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't appeal to him enough, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, ultimately, what part of Kunimi\Ndid you fall for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do by knowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really. Sheer curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choco-Coronet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to go get you one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring a lunch one day,\Nand Kunimi gave me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first term of our first year.\NThe first day I tried to buy some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was overwhelmed,\Nwhen Kunimi called out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, so you like sweet things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said, as he ate his battle trophy,\Nthe curry bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The curry bread prince, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much is a Choco-Coronet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,130 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your price is quite reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have fallen in love\Nif it was you who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's his face, in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was timing, in the end, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was feeling rather down back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch, if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have a Futaba\Nstaying over at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you were\Nacting strange on the phone last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I first thought, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I talk to you like this,\Nyou're both really Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's my other self's opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something about quantum teleportation,\Nif that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her observation was that your consciousness\Nis what is perceiving you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and there are two copies of your mind\Nfor one reason or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you believed a lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think it's a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have a clue as to why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't make a difference\Nof who to ask, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to do club stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X and Y here are inside the parentheses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making coffee, want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede is the little sister, so honey café au lait\Nwith lots of milk and honey is her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be delighted to have\Nwhat Kaede-san is having.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I might do the same, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kaede-chan.\NIt looks like it's from my manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this a good time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for your hard work\Nfilming up to yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you away from home, by chance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm at my boyfriend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see, boyfriend...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, what!? Boyfriend!?\ND-Did you just say "boyfriend"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba was around until\Na few minutes ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right after the game started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does Futaba come by often?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see. I think every so often,\Non the way to or from the Science Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows which is actually "on the way"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happened to Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like school enough\Nto come during summer break, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning something happened to Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi-senpai, the coach is calling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me up if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me. Better fly over,\Neven in the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can fly,\Nso I'll race over on my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, Azusagawa residence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, can you do that one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Azusagawa residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say it more like a newlywed wife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so giddy\Nover one phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How are things on your end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba was here at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She's been here the whole time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyways, can you come home soon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got a call from my manager earlier,\Nso there's something I want to talk to you about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll see you later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa, you're friends\Nwith that girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By "that girl",\NI take it you mean Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that girl doing something pretty risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is her hidden account.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Big Brother.\NWhat a rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:25:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Time\N#8 Wash It All Away on a Stormy Night
